show.title: Oops, Not A Gold Digger

show.sharing_text_v2:
हेलो! मैंने Kuku FM (Android)  पर यह शो सुना और मुझे यकीन है कि आपको भी यह जरूर पसंद आएगा। 
https://links.kukufm.com/WyyuaA
show.description: When spirited delivery girl Disha rescues feisty Suman Dadi from a taxi spat, she has no idea it will lead to an accidental marriage with charming yet mysterious Vikrant, a man she thinks is just a broke caretaker, but who’s actually heir to a billionaire empire. Between office politics, spoiled rivals like Tia, hidden identities, and Dadi’s matchmaking mischief, Disha must protect her dreams, her dignity, and maybe her heart. Watch Now!
